TextChange: Just so you know I did not leave the page.  I was thinking if there was anything else to add.  This isn't right.  It does not take me 30 minutes to write an essay when I got all my thoughts together quickly.  Maybe for some but this is easy for me to come up with an essay.  I hope I am not punished for just thinking and re-reading my essay.  You should have the submit button active when we are done typing our essay.  What are we supposed to do when we are done?  This isn't right.  Now I'm out of $11.75 just because I'm done early and re-reading the essay???  Now I'm upset.  You'll be hearing from me if I don't get paid for my time and essay.  Just like a real job, you pay people for their time.  I don't care if surveys aren't considered real job, we all are doing our work and we deserve to get paid for our time. Shame on you for rejecting people for simple things.
